I didn't know
they were your trees.

939
01:10:13,175 --> 01:10:16,110
No, they're Mick's.

940
01:10:16,212 --> 01:10:18,476
I'm helping him unload.

941
01:10:19,582 --> 01:10:23,348
- How are Mick and Alida?
- Fine.

942
01:10:23,452 --> 01:10:27,479
Will you say hello
to them for me?

943
01:10:27,590 --> 01:10:31,754
They'll be right back.
They're doing some christmas shopping.

944
01:10:31,860 --> 01:10:33,885
Here's a medium-sized fir,
Mrs. Scott.

945
01:10:33,996 --> 01:10:37,796
Or maybe you'd rather have a spruce?

946
01:10:39,101 --> 01:10:44,038
- A silver tip spruce?
- Oh, i've got a beauty!

947
01:10:44,139 --> 01:10:47,802
You remembered.
Oh, Cary...

948
01:10:47,910 --> 01:10:51,744
Ron! Ron?

949
01:10:51,847 --> 01:10:53,781
Mick and Alida sent me
to get you.

950
01:10:55,584 --> 01:10:58,985
Oh, I didn't know
you had a customer.

951
